text: Hello. I own a small agency that supports websites for about 45 small businesses. Most are micro businesses with fewer than four FTEs. For some, I just host the site and for others, I'm involved with day-to-date site updates and marketing efforts. My primary goal here is to learn more about SEO for these small businesses, some of which have multiple locations in the same state.
